'''PL Kyodan''' o '''Iglesia di Libertat Perfekto''' (パーフェクト リバティー教団, Pāfekuto Ribatī Kyōdan) ta un movementu religioso internashonal ku a desaroyá fo'i kultura zen [[Budismo|budista]] di [[Hapon]] den komienso di siglo 20. Su fundadó ta Tokuharu Miki (1871–1938). Meta di PL Kyodan ta pa trese paz mundial.<ref>Church of Perfect Liberty,[https://web.archive.org/web/20170411043321/http://www.perfectliberty.ca/whatispl.php   What is PL?], Canada </ref> PL ta prediká ku "bida ta arte" i ku sernan humano a nase pa ekspresá nan propio individualidat den tur kos e hasi, asina "kreando arte real". Pa yuda mehora bida di e kreyentenan i pa superá nan privashon nan e patriarka (oshieoya-sama) i su saserdotenan ta instruí nan tokante nan problemanan i ta guia nan pa solusiona esakinan.  

== Preseptonan == 
PL no ta posee un buki dibino (manera un [[beibel]]), sino PL ta dispone di 21 preseptonan, kual a keda promulga dia 29 di september 1947 dor di Tokuchika Miki. Esakinan ta forma e doktrina basiko di e movementu.<ref name="PLHistory">Church of Perfect Liberty,[https://web.archive.org/web/20140205014641/http://web.perfect-liberty.or.jp/history.html  PL History] (11 yuli 1996)</ref>

* 1. Bida ta arte 
* 2. Man's bida ta un succession di self-expressions 
* 3. Homber ta un manifestation di Dios 
* 4. Homber suffers si e homber fails na ekspresá mes 
* 5. Man's rason mes ta lost kuandu swayed desde sintimentu í emotions 
* 6. Man's rason mes ta revealed kuandu djé ego ta effaced 
* 7. Henter kosnan existí den mutual relationship na un otro 
* 8. Biba radiantly ban e solo 
* 9. Henter homber ta igual 
* 10. Strive pa creating mutual felisidat 
* 11. Tin rason fe den Dios 
* 12. Tin un kaminda (funshion) strabagante na kada "name" (existensha) 
* 13. Tin un kaminda pa homber, í tin otro pa muhenan 
* 14. Henter ta pa mundu pas 
* 15. Henter ta un spil 
* 16. Henter kosnan mehorashon í develop 
* 17. Comprehend ta ki mas essential 
* 18. Na kada momentu homber stands na e crossroads di bon í evil 
* 19. Aktua kuandu bo intuition dictates 
* 20. Biba den un maestro unidat di mente í afèr 
* 21. Biba den maestro liberty


